Package org.forgerock.openam.authentication.modules.common

Class JaspiAuthModuleWrapper<T extends javax.security.auth.message.module.ServerAuthModule>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.authentication.modules.common.JaspiAuthModuleWrapper<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Implementation of the ServerAuthModule interface.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PersistentCookieModuleWrapper
    public abstract class JaspiAuthModuleWrapper<T extends javax.security.auth.message.module.ServerAuthModule>
extends Object
    Base class for wrapping a Jaspi ServerAuthModule. Provides wrappers over the modules functionality, and hides the underlying code from external users.
